<title>INDIA: Indian Aluminium to invest 1.7bln rupees.</title>
<headline>Indian Aluminium to invest 1.7bln rupees.</headline>
<dateline>BOMBAY 1997-05-19</dateline>
<text>
<p>Indian Aluminum Company Ltd plans to invest 1.7 billion rupees in 1997/98 (April-March), senior company officials told reporters on Monday in the eastern city of Calcutta.</p>
<p>The company will invest the amount for modernisation and upgradation of its various plants in India, officials said.</p>
<p>It did not give any details.</p>
